'''Silvia Abravanel Pedroso de Abreu''' (born in [[São Paulo]], 18 April 1971) is a [[Brazilians|Brazilian]] [[Television producer|producer]], [[TV presenter]] and [[television director]].
She is the second daughter of the Brazilian television mogul [[Silvio Santos]] and his deceased wife Maria Aparecida Abravanel, and because this she is nicknamed for your father as "Filha Número Dois" (Daughter number two). When Aparecida don´t can have children, she was adopted.<ref>{{cite web|title=Silvia Abravanel: "Tenho o maior orgulho de ser filha adotiva"|url=http://revistaquem.globo.com/QUEM-News/noticia/2015/07/silvia-abravanel-tenho-o-maior-orgulho-de-ser-filha-adotiva.html|work=Revista quem|access-date=9 November 2015}}</ref> With her death, Silvio married with the writer [[Íris Abravanel]] and after this, Silvia began to call her by mother when she was 4 years old.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rd1.ig.com.br/silvia-abravanel-revela-magoa-de-gugu-e-rejeita-amizade-do-loiro-saiu-sem-dar-tchau/|title=Silvia Abravanel revela mágoa que tem de Gugu e aproveita o programa da Eliana para demonstrar carinho a Silvio Santos, que a adotou aos 3 anos.|accessdate=27 July 2015|author=Luiz Fábio Almeida|publisher=RD1}}</ref> Silvia is the sister of the [[Sistema Brasileiro de Televisão|SBT]]'s artistic director, Daniela, of the TV hosts Patrícia and Rebecca, who also have the same work as your. Along this she have two sisters Cintia and Renata. Her nephew [[Tiago Abravanel]] is also a respected actor in [[Brazil]]. All of them work on [[Grupo Silvio Santos]] and on SBT.
Silvia is married to the country singer Edu Pedroso.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://celebridades.uol.com.br/album/2013/12/06/filha-de-silvio-santos-se-casa-com-cantor-sertanejo-veja-fotos.htm|title=Filha de Silvio Santos se casa com cantor sertanejo; veja fotos|accessdate=24 December 2013|author=Equipe UOL Entretenimento|publisher=[[Universo Online|UOL]] Celebridades}}</ref> She is the mother of two girls: Amanda and the firstborn Luana, who suffers from [[galactosemia]] (genetic disease characterized by the inability of metabolize [[galactose]], the typical sugar in milk) and from a [[neurological deficit]] caused by a delay in [[childbirth]]. Both daughters are from previous marriages.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://caras.uol.com.br/tv/silvia-abravanel-orgulho-ser-filha-adotiva-silvio-santos-diretora-sbt-bom-dia-e-cia#.ViRiTdWrRR1|title=Silvia Abravanel abre o coração: 'Tenho o maior orgulho por ter sido adotada'|date=27 July 2015|publisher=[[CARAS]]|accessdate=19 October 2015}}</ref>
